Preconditions:
- The input array `nums` is not null.
- The length of the input array `nums` is greater than or equal to 1.
- All elements in the input array `nums` are positive integers.

Postconditions:
- The method returns an integer representing the total number of good partitions of the input array `nums`.
- The returned value is non-negative.
- The returned value is less than or equal to <code>10<sup>9</sup> + 7</code>.